{
  "date": "2026-03-23",
  "title": "Built to Be Poured Out",
  "scriptures": [
    {
      "ref": "Ephesians 2:10",
      "text": "For we are His workmanship, created in Christ Jesus for good works, which God prepared beforehand, that we should walk in them."
    }
  ],
  "sections": [
    {
      "key": "read_this_out_loud",
      "label": "Read This Out Loud",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "You weren’t saved to sit."
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "You were shaped to serve."
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "God didn’t just rescue you from something."
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "He designed you for something."
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "You don’t find purpose by thinking about it."
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "You find it by stepping into it."
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "You’re not random."
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "You’re wired with intention."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "key": "devotional",
      "label": "The Devotional",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "Most men are waiting to feel ready."
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "But God never called you to feel ready."
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "He called you to be available."
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "Romans 12 says we all have different gifts."
        },
        {
          "type": "lines",
          "items": [
            "Different strengths.",
            "Different roles.",
            "Different assignments."
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "But the same expectation:"
        },
        {
          "type": "callout",
          "prefix": "👉",
          "text": "Use what you’ve been given."
        },
        {
          "type": "lines",
          "items": [
            "Not someday.",
            "Not when life slows down.",
            "Now."
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "Because your wiring is not accidental."
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "It’s assignment-specific."
        },
        {
          "type": "lines",
          "items": [
            "Some build.",
            "Some lead.",
            "Some encourage.",
            "Some give.",
            "Some carry burdens others can’t."
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "But all are meant to contribute."
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "And here’s the danger."
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "When you don’t use what God put in you…"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "You don’t just delay purpose."
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "You drift from it."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "key": "shift",
      "label": "The Shift",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "A lot of men think:"
        },
        {
          "type": "lines",
          "items": [
            "“I just need to grow more first.”",
            "“I’m not equipped yet.”",
            "“I’ll step in later.”"
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "But Hebrews 13 says something powerful:"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "God equips you as you go."
        },
        {
          "type": "lines",
          "items": [
            "Not before.",
            "Not after."
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "callout",
          "prefix": "👉",
          "text": "In motion."
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "Which means waiting isn’t preparation."
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "Obedience is."
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "And the longer you wait to step in…"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "The easier it becomes to stay on the sidelines."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "key": "jesus_set_the_pattern",
      "label": "Jesus Set the Pattern",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "Jesus didn’t just teach truth."
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "He moved toward need."
        },
        {
          "type": "lines",
          "items": [
            "He healed.",
            "He served.",
            "He showed up.",
            "He poured out."
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "Over and over again."
        },
        {
          "type": "lines",
          "items": [
            "Not when it was convenient.",
            "Not when it was scheduled."
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "But when it was in front of Him."
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "Because purpose is rarely found in theory."
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "It’s found in response."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "key": "truth",
      "label": "The Truth",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "You don’t discover your purpose sitting still."
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "You discover it by using what’s already in your hands."
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "And if you keep holding back…"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "You don’t protect your capacity…"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "You waste it."
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "You weren’t built to spectate."
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "You were built to pour out."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "key": "reflection",
      "label": "Reflection",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "bullet_list",
          "items": [
            "Where am I holding back what God has already given me?",
            "What gift, strength, or instinct have I been underusing?",
            "Where is God inviting me to step in right now?"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "key": "declaration",
      "label": "Declaration",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "I am not waiting to be ready."
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "I am already equipped for what God has placed in front of me."
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "I will use what I’ve been given and trust God to meet me in motion."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "key": "action_step",
      "label": "Action Step",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "Today, don’t overthink your role."
        },
        {
          "type": "lines",
          "items": [
            "👉 Use what’s in your hands.",
            "👉 Step into one opportunity to serve.",
            "👉 Move toward a need instead of away from it."
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "lines",
          "items": [
            "Encourage someone.",
            "Help someone.",
            "Lead something.",
            "Initiate something."
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "Just don’t sit on it."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "key": "one_sentence_to_carry",
      "label": "One Sentence to Carry",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "quote",
          "text": "“I was built to pour out, not hold back.”"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "- TheWrkShop"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
